welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Poulsbo, the charming city known for its Scandinavian heritage and breathtaking views of the Puget Sound. We invite you to explore our quaint shops, delicious restaurants, and immerse yourself in our unique culture. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport serves as the primary hub for all flights.

terminals.name: Seaplane Terminal
terminals.description: The seaplane terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport is used for all seaplane flights departing and arriving at the airport.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bremerton Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport houses all commercial flights and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The General Aviation Terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport caters to private and charter flights, providing personalized services for passengers and crew members.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is a modern and efficient facility, serving both commercial and general aviation flights.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: The North Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport primarily serves private and corporate aviation, with a range of amenities and services available for passengers.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is used for cargo and freight operations, with state-of-the-art facilities and equipment to handle a variety of goods.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport terminal.
